    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 15th level, you have learned how to chastise anyone who dares wield beguilements against you and your wards. Whenever you or a creature you can see within 30 feet of you succeeds on an Intelligence, a Wisdom, or a Charisma saving throw, you can use your reaction to deal your paladin level + your Charisma modifier (minimum of 1) force damage to the creature that forced the saving throw.</p><p>If a creature under the effect of your Watcher's Will succeeds the saving throw, then you can also Divine Smite to to deal additional force damage as part of the same reaction.</p>",
